Ever wonder what happens to tech after you donate it? I got an EXCLUSIVE behind the scenes tour of Goodwill Computer Works to see the entire process from donation dropoff to store shelves. Then I put their tech bargains to the test - are these gadgets really worth your money or just electronic junk?
